name: Adipati Karna with Konta Jaya
description: This character is taken from the Mahabharata story. Konta Jaya's weapon belongs to Adipati Karna. Konta's gift weapon is from Lord Indra. Konta Jaya is a very powerful weapon but can only be used once. At first this weapon was used to kill Arjuna, but this weapon was used to kill Gatot Kaca.
